Class ElementWrapper

java.lang.Object
  org.hibernate.tuple.ElementWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, org.dom4j.Branch, org.dom4j.Element, org.dom4j.Node
public class ElementWrapper
extends Object
implements org.dom4j.Element, Serializable

Wraps dom4j elements, allowing them to exist in a non-hierarchical structure.
